trans-unit.source: Represents a user or user-group for granting access to rights managed content.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en bruker eller brukergruppe for å gi tilgang til rettigheter behandlet innhold.

trans-unit.source: As with other <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement> types, ContentUser is only usable in full trust applications.
trans-unit.target: Som med andre <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement>typer ContentUser brukes bare i fullstendig klarering programmer.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The user or group `name` is often in the form of an individual e-mail address (such as johndoe@contoso.com) or an e-mail distribution list (such as marketing@contoso.com).
trans-unit.target: Brukeren eller gruppen `name` er ofte i form av en enkelt e-postadresse (eksempel johndoe@contoso.com) eller en distribusjonsliste (eksempel marketing@contoso.com).

trans-unit.source: The user or group name.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på brukeren eller gruppen.

trans-unit.source: The method for authentication.
trans-unit.target: Metode for godkjenning.

trans-unit.source: Gets an instance of the "Anyone" <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser"></xref> persona.
trans-unit.target: Henter en forekomst av "Alle" <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser"> </xref> personene.

trans-unit.source: AnyoneUser has <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser.AuthenticationType%2A> "Internal" and <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser.Name%2A> "Anyone".
trans-unit.target: AnyoneUser har <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser.AuthenticationType%2A>"Interne" og <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser.Name%2A>"Alle".</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser.Name%2A> </xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser.AuthenticationType%2A>

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser.AuthenticationType%2A> "Internal" with <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser.Name%2A> "Anyone" is granted rights during publishing, the authentication server will issue a <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense> to any request and will attach the license to the requesting user.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser.AuthenticationType%2A>"Interne" med <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser.Name%2A>"Alle" gis rights under publisering, godkjenningsserveren utsteder en <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>til en forespørsel, og vil knytte lisensen til brukeren som anmoder.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense> </xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser.Name%2A> </xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser.AuthenticationType%2A>

trans-unit.target: En forekomst av "Alle" <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser"> </xref> personene.

trans-unit.source: After a user has been authenticated and IsAuthenticated is `true`, the user dialog and prompt to confirm authentication is no longer displayed when creating a <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.SecureEnvironment>.
trans-unit.target: Når en bruker er godkjent, og IsAuthenticated er `true`, brukerdialogboksen og bedt om å bekrefte godkjenning vises ikke lenger når du oppretter en <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.SecureEnvironment>.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.SecureEnvironment>

trans-unit.source: OwnerUser is used by the server-side templates to give special rights to the content author or publisher when the protected document is created.
trans-unit.target: OwnerUser brukes av serversiden malene for å gi noen rettigheter til innhold forfatteren eller utgiveren når beskyttede dokumentet er opprettet.
